lead_paragraph: SOMEWHERE IN NEW GUINEA, Sept. 30 (Delayed) -- The slow and cautious advance of Australian units on the main Port Moresby-Buna trail, which leads over the high mountains of Central New Guinea, continues.
abstract: Allied planes bomb Salamaua and Buna
